title: These songs just turned 20, and it’s a tough blow for egos everywhere (20 Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
I remember when I thought I was old and mature back in middle school, and it’s clear to see now that I may’ve overestimated myself on all accounts. 20 years later, I realize just how much I’ve changed since the days when these hit songs were released in the year 1997. I mean ‘Tubthumping’ by Chumbawamba was the shit, man. Obviously it wasn’t, but that just proves my point. 
I digress… 
The Verve –“Bitter Sweet Symphony” (Seen Above) 2
